snippet.title: GRNDLW
snippet.description:
Howdy! I'm Grind. On my channel you can find bunch of music videos full of scenes and sync's from the movies. I'm so glad to do these videos. If you want to support me, to be able make a much more better videos. Don't forget to Subscribe  my channel. It helps a lot! ;)       

Special thanks to Evelyn Jackson!
